lead_paragraph: Everton's League Cup upset at the hands of second tier Norwich City on Tuesday was overshadowed by the rare sight of the Goodison Park faithful giving a standing ovation to an opposing striker scoring against the home side.

headline.print_headline: Naismith Earns Goodison Cheers Despite Helping Sink Everton
